defaultWe are therefore supportive of an approach to the tariff cap which considers both the 
defaultCarbon Floor Price (
defaultCPF
default)
default and 
defaultEmissions Trading Scheme (
defaultETS
default)
default as part of the calculation of the cap, as this brings the price of support up to levels which would be more ef
defaultfective for driving the uptake of GSHPs. GSHPs are an important technology to deliver Government Heat Strategy projections and drive EU targets, and it is therefore right to offer a level of support to drive the market for this technology, and in turn brin
defaultg the capital costs of installation down.  
